latestPosts.caption: A bit of this, a bit of that 📸

Still buzzing from the best birthday ever! 🥳✨ Huge shoutout to everyone who showed up and went all out with their costumes—it was everything I dreamed of and more. We had Aladdin bringing the charm, Cruella with the sass, Silver Surfer shining bright, Boss Baby bossing around, Ursula serving drama, Morticia bringing the elegance, Nobita being all cute, Mario with the iconic moves, Johnny Bravo and his swagger, and Shaun the Sheep just being adorable! 🖤 You guys brought all the nostalgia, laughs, and love, and I couldn’t be more grateful. Adulthood is way more fun when it’s this animated! 💫
